I"#<h2 id="plot-summary">Plot Summary</h2>

<p><em>Jodu Daktarer Patient</em> is the story of a thrilling surgry as told by an aging and experiences surgeon. The stage for the story is set at the weekly conference of <em>Calcutta Physisurgic Club</em>. After a lecture by Dr. Harish Chakladar on the determinent of death, Dr. Jodu, the president of <em>Calcutta Physisurgic Club</em>, is called upon to present his views on the subject. Then, Dr. Jodu, goes on to ellaborately describe the thrilling case surgery he performed a few decades ago.</p>

